node.text:
I’ll try almost anything once (if it’s legal and doesn’t hurt anyone of course 😂) being on TV has never been a goal of mine but a single episode seemed doable and I’m pleased to share I didn’t even totally hate watching myself back!!!! I’m excited to share a peek into my life and design process in the new show “point of view: a designer profile” on @magnolianetwork. you can stream it now on @discoveryplus! 
.
Watch it for the clover and pop pop cameos, the behind the scenes of pulling @gaiahousecafe_gr together and @rupertsamuel stealing the show and my heart all over again. 
.
#magnolianetwork

node.text:
our guest bathroom ✨ 
.
complete with a couple diy projects from my bag of tricks. this is the first bathroom I got to use our own “sss quarterline” cabinet fronts from my line with @semihandmade on a vanity, which makes this maybe my most epic ikea hack to date?! 
I also used the wood appliance pulls from my hardware line for @parkstudio_la as drawer pulls for their extra large size. and shall we talk about the gorgeous jumbo @alliedmaker sconce? #sssinteriors #samuelfamilyfixer

the guest room, aka my nap room, is truly one of my favorite spots in the house now. I may or may not slip down here in the middle of the night to sleep when Archie sneaks into our bed (you know I do and it is glorious 😂). swipe for the before. slightly different angle but she’s come along way. #sssinteriors #samuelfamilyfixer 
.
